title: Weekly Review with Clay and Buck H2 - Dec 4 2021

description:
How important is natural immunity? According to "Mr. I Am Science" Fauci: We don't know. New York brings back useless masks to fight Omicron. Where is the data on masking? Without data, it isn't science, it's superstition. DeSantis: Covid lockdowns, mandates ‘not going to happen’ in Florida. Pfizer CEO says "most likely scenario" is going to be "annual revaccination." Covid is making Big Pharma a lot of money! Comedian and podcaster, Adam Carolla joins C&B to give his take on comedy in a woke world and his new show, "Truth Yeller." Sec. Buttigieg: If you buy an expensive electric vehicle, you "will never have to worry about gas prices again."
